docs.title: Commands
docs.text:
• mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project.
  • mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server.
  • mkdocs build - Build the documentation site.
  • mkdocs -h - Print help message and exit.

docs.title: Project layout
docs.text:
mkdocs.yml    # The configuration file.
docs/
    index.md  # The documentation homepage.
    ...       # Other markdown pages, images and other files.

docs.title: Nisar Safi
docs.text:
Front-End Developer

With a passion for crafting engaging and dynamic web experiences, I am a Front-End Developer specializing in HTML, CSS, and JavaScript technologies. With proficiency in frameworks such as Tailwind CSS, Bootstrap, and jQuery, I bring creativity and efficiency to every project I undertake.

Having honed my skills over one and a half years of professional experience, I have collaborated with diverse teams, leveraging my expertise to deliver high-quality solutions. My ability to translate design concepts into responsive and intuitive user interfaces has been instrumental in the success of numerous projects.

Equipped with a keen eye for detail and a commitment to staying updated with the latest industry trends, I am dedicated to pushing boundaries and continuously refining my craft. Whether it's optimizing performance, enhancing accessibility, or ensuring cross-browser compatibility, I thrive on overcoming challenges and delivering exceptional results.

I am eager to contribute my skills and expertise to innovative projects, furthering my growth as a front-end developer while making meaningful contributions to the digital landscape.

Hourly Rate: 67 💰
